Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果姐姐隱瞞了什麼 你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比如在甲州勝沼時 明明援軍不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卻必須命令部下戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤勇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼突然說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我會跟隨你的 無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為姐姐是唯一的家人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把黑板上的三句話分別分節試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-16\pos(959.785,646.285)}咖哩喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-45\pos(564,837)}吃我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,比較像勇者部的文化祭節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,結城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是沒什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那能請你讀出現在講到的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上課時請切斷電源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 停下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 不是吧 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 大家都怪怪的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 好好聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是… 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這一天 我們的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,暫時 結束了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我又睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,疼 似乎不是在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,畫面變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩 小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,總算找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩 小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你們兩個都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸中的萬幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個要是沒有拿著手機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個app還有這種功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,隱藏功能？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這個隱藏功能是產生這種情況時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,自動啟動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 好方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個app 是入部時風前輩要我們下載的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷靜下來聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大赦派來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 大赦是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,供奉神樹大人的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼特別任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我還是第一次聽說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒被選中 我是打算就這樣瞞過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的班 讚州中學勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,被選中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在看到的這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是神樹大人造出的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼… 不是什麼壞的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是 被神樹大人選中的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,必須在這裡面和敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個點是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,幸虧是個慢速的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,浮在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs29.997\bord2.997\pos(1023,982.503)}Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是宿命點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了殺死世界而攻過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命點的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到達世界的恩惠 神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候 世界就會死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界裡 只有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,通過大赦的調查 你們被判斷為最有資質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.78,Notice,,0,0,0,,全市鄉鎮中學 勇者資質報告書 機密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會… 怎麼可能和那種東西戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,辦法是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只要表現出戰鬥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這個app的功能就會解鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,從而成為神樹大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,盯上我們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已經發現我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥什麼的 不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上東鄉逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,樹也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼能扔下姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我會跟隨你的 無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 樹 跟我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是被神樹大人選中的勇者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是守護這個世界的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,通過神樹大人的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,會把力量借給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,坐雲宵飛車啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把手舉起來 表現出戰鬥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎… 出來了什麼武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現在在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,比起擔心我 你那邊沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,數量太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉 抱歉瞞著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩是為大家著想才沒說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一個人沒法挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是正符合勇者部的活動目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是風前輩的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 小樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 不要管我 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼話 怎麼能把朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下朋友不管什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我絕對做不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡捨棄朋友的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,留下痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓大家留下那種回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:21:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是踴躍地助人為樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是讚州中學勇者部 結城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成為勇者！
